pin2.name: Printer Cart
pin2.description: This beautiful printer cart is small but has lots of organization. The small cart is great for a small office, but pretty enough for storing a printer in any room. The sliding plexiglass door can cover up areas that are not needed.

pin4.name: Strawberry Pie
pin4.description: This homemade strawberry pie is an old-fashioned favorite. Sweet, juicy strawberries, flaky pastry and a scoop of vanilla ice cream make this baked strawberry pie the perfect dessert for strawberry season.

pin5.description: Create a production-ready stop for your miter saw station, router table, or table saw miter gauge with this heavy-duty stop. It features dual cursors and durable construction that give it accuracy and toughness in one easy-to-use stop.
